### Escambia County, Florida

This document pertains specifically to the county situated in Florida. For clarity, if you’re looking for its counterpart across the state line in Alabama, that would be [Escambia County, Alabama](/Escambia_County,_Alabama). And should your interest lie with the waterway that lends its name, you’ll want to consult the entry for the [Escambia River](/Escambia_River).

